      <h3><a href="#1"><i class="fa fa-link"></i></a>How does Jackschess help me as a player?</h3>
      <p>Jackschess gives you the ability to connect with any chess player in the world and all the necissary tools, all in one screen, to create the perfect online chess environemnt. Not only can you review with coaches 1 on 1 or in groups, but you can also hop on to review a game you just played with your opponent, show your friends all over the world your last tourney games, etc.</p>
      <p>There is a big disconnect between the learning expierence you get in person with other players and what you get online from sites like chess.com, ICC, chess24, etc. No matter how good technology gets, Tactics Trainer will never be as good as a titled player reviewing your games and openings with you. Jackschess brings that in person expierence to the internet.</p>
